Write a Java program to find LCM of two Numbers.(07 Nov18. Write a Java program to count the number of digits of an integer


import java.util.Scanner;

public class NumberOfDigitsInInteger {


    public static void main(String []args)
    {
        Scanner scan=new Scanner(System.in);
        System.out.println("Enter Number:");
        int n=scan.nextInt();
        int count=0;
        while(n!=0)
        {
            n=n/10;
            count++;
        }
        System.out.println("Number of digits:"+count);
    }
    
}
Output:
Enter Number:
12345
Number of digits:5
